On behalf of our valued client, CBRE is excited to present to the market for sale via Expressions of Interest, 12 Trade Street, Lytton. This prime investment opportunity is situated within the tightly held Industrial hub of Lytton which is part of the Southern Tradecoast area. Lytton is located approx. 19klms from the Brisbane CBD, approx. 12klms from the Brisbane Airport and on the doorstep of the Port of Brisbane. This area is very popular amongst a number of logistics and distribution occupiers due to its key infrastructure and location; some of these users include K-Mart, Yusen Logistics, Silk, Toll, Toyota just to name a few.


This site is improved by a 1,540sqm office/warehouse facility which offers the following key features:


•	370sqm recently refurbished office accommodation split over two levels
•	1,170sqm warehouse split over three individual buildings
•	4,223sqm General Industry zoned site
•	Large concrete hardstand for external storage/container set down
•	36% site cover (approx)
•	Value add opportunity 
•	Fully fenced and secured site
•	Property offers huge exposure to Port of Brisbane Motorway


This property is being offered For Sale via Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 5th March 2020 at 4pm AEST. (If not sold prior).

For further information regarding this prime port investment or to arrange your inspection, please contact Exclusive Agents, Zac Ryan or Ben Lyons of CBRE.

The property incorporates approximately 400sqm of well-appointed office accommodation split over two levels.
